<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>58</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>kě wàng zì yóu 迦南58</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 kě wàng zì yóu, kě wàng ān níng kě wàng rén shì jiān dōu chōng mǎn zhǔ ài.
 hēi àn de de fāng, xū yào guāng míng, zhēng zhàn de de fāng, xū yào hé píng,
 yuàn zuò ài de shǐ zhě, jiāng zhǔ ài sǎ jìn rén de xīn zhōng,
 yuàn zuò hé píng. de shǐ zhě, qù fèng xiàn zì jǐ de rén shēng.</lyrics>
</song>